short.pt_BR: Encontre e organize suas buscas do Chat GPT.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Struggling to keep track of your Chat GPT conversations and searches? Introducing our Chrome extension, designed specifically for Chat GPT users like you! Effortlessly organize and access your interactions, no matter when you last engaged. Elevate your Chat GPT experience to the next level!
